ets/steam/apps/1714910/extras/34ee2c0eddc35d6c8f51c8f48befb569.poster.avif?t=1758714986\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714910/extras/34ee2c0eddc35d6c8f51c8f48befb569.webm?t=1758714986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714910/extras/34ee2c0eddc35d6c8f51c8f48befb569.mp4?t=1758714986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Levels are<strong> fast-paced, tense </strong>and always full of <strong>SLAPS!</strong>",
